Package com.project.moviebooking.dto

package com.project.moviebooking.dto
The "dto" (Data Transfer Object) package contains data structures used for transferring data between different layers of the movie booking application.

DTOs within this package represent simplified and serializable objects that facilitate the exchange of data between the presentation layer, service layer, and external interfaces. These objects often mirror specific subsets of entity attributes to fulfill specific functionality or communication requirements.

Organizing DTOs in this package helps in maintaining separation of concerns, enhancing modularity, and ensuring clean data transfer across various parts of the movie booking system.
